<section class="tw-rfeat">
  <div class="tw-container">
    <div class="tw-rfeat-card">
      <div class="tw-rfeat-img">
        <div class="tw-rfeat-mock">
          <div class="tw-rfeat-mock-eye">FREE FOR BOARDS &middot; V3</div>
          <div class="tw-rfeat-mock-title">The HOA Board Playbook</div>
          <div class="tw-rfeat-mock-rule"></div>
          <div class="tw-rfeat-mock-lines">
            <i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i>
          </div>
          <div class="tw-rfeat-mock-foot">32 pages &middot; Reserves &middot; Vendor &middot; Cadence</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tw-rfeat-body">
        <div class="tw-eyebrow">Featured Download</div>
        <h2 class="tw-rfeat-title">The HOA Board Playbook<br/><em>battle-tested across 300+ Mid-Atlantic communities.</em></h2>
        <p class="tw-rfeat-copy">A 32-page field guide to running a board without burning out. Written by Tidewater&rsquo;s PCAM-credentialed managers from what we&rsquo;ve actually seen on agendas, not theory.</p>
        <ul class="tw-rfeat-bullets">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Reserve funding before Maryland made it law &mdash; and what we&rsquo;d still recommend</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>The vendor compliance file every board should keep (and how to audit yours)</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Meeting cadence templates by community size, with sample agendas</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>How to read your monthly management report in 10 minutes</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <form class="tw-rfeat-form">
          <input type="email" placeholder="your-board-email@community.org" required />
          <button class="tw-btn tw-btn-primary tw-btn-pill" type="submit">Email me the playbook</button>
        </form>
        <p class="tw-rfeat-fine">Free. No sales call attached. One follow-up email a quarter, unsubscribe any time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
